{"tid":2057563,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"長實集團不擔心港區國安法推出後有走資潮","createTime":"2020-06-09T13:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T17:48:16.000Z","uid":162303,"like":9,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"79d50672b7959dfc5cfe49bc999d080ccba073a0","tid":2057563,"uid":162303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T13:05:00.000Z","msg":"長實集團(<a href=\"http://01113.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01113.HK&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7Xelq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=e52b256a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01113.HK</a>)趙國雄：不擔心港區國安法推出後有走資潮 料下半年整體樓市穩定 <br />\n長實集團(<a href=\"http://01113.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01113.HK&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7Xelq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=e52b256a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01113.HK</a>)  +1.050 (+2.246%)    沽空 $9.02千萬; 比率 22.688%   執行董事趙國雄在發布會後表示，雖然未知港區國安法的詳情，但個人認為是有必須要有的，因為社會安定時市民才會感安心，對樓市而言是正面影響。他不擔心條例推出後有走資潮，即使部分市民選擇移民，亦未必會放售單位。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，中美貿易糾紛對本港樓市一直有陰影，隨著貿易協議第一階段協議落實，對全球經濟都有正面影響。他料本港樓價上半年有5至8%調整，下半年香港經濟穩定下來後，整體樓市亦會穩定，升幅則要視乎個別樓盤而定。"},{"pid":"1802675a20ee426e30ca69bc4c536f5ea09b5ef2","tid":2057563,"uid":76216,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"佢都走曬啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed77f51ef49c5582182e663ccce5154b2ec5414b","tid":2057563,"uid":37596,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"自己走左仲講不擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6959283ff3173827847e07eca7b3fa8425b9f1ee","tid":2057563,"uid":305083,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T13:06:47.000Z","msg":"最先走果個就係誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38717ebdd0a77ba3d98b7d57b91fe5fecbc34587","tid":2057563,"uid":343161,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T13:07:44.000Z","msg":"長實：關我撚事咩"},{"pid":"21932