66afd0c320a3b2c9b2904e","tid":2057563,"uid":19353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:32:33.000Z","msg":"我都唔擔心 因為我都走晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae284a77070f2345650ad79b9cdb8b9326b3f93","tid":2057563,"uid":274330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79d50672b7959dfc5cfe49bc999d080ccba073a0","tid":2057563,"uid":162303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T13:05:00.000Z","msg":"長實集團(<a href=\"http://01113.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01113.HK&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7Xelq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=e52b256a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01113.HK</a>)趙國雄：不擔心港區國安法推出後有走資潮 料下半年整體樓市穩定 <br />\n長實集團(<a href=\"http://01113.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01113.HK&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7Xelq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=e52b256a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01113.HK</a>)  +1.050 (+2.246%)    沽空 $9.02千萬; 比率 22.688%   執行董事趙國雄在發布會後表示，雖然未知港區國安法的詳情，但個人認為是有必須要有的，因為社會安定時市民才會感安心，對樓市而言是正面影響。他不擔心條例推出後有走資潮，即使部分市民選擇移民，亦未必會放售單位。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，中美貿易糾紛對本港樓市一直有陰影，隨著貿易協議第一階段協議落實，對全球經濟都有正面影響。他料本港樓價上半年有5至8%調整，下半年香港經濟穩定下來後，整體樓市亦會穩定，升幅則要視乎個別樓盤而定。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:41:15.000Z","msg":"因為國安法推出前已經走哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf6cca9b35d6764204fb38fc2664d5cf68aa8d7","tid":2057563,"uid":194120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:00:42.000Z","msg":"真係要買嘅買1號仔好過1113"},{"pid":"3bd88bcee2a6b4403ebdc84789fdf3ac0d484d7e","tid":2057563,"uid":44171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:01:45.000Z","msg":"幾時全家放棄加拿大國籍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1619eafdb72c22acb87d6e32d091199d25aef04e","tid":2057563,"uid":248373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:36:46.00